{"tid":1659074,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全球最大 YOUTUBER PEWDIEPIE 關注香港議題","createTime":"2019-10-16T18:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T16:15:38.000Z","uid":317990,"like":135,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"4172a75e0fe47f03cf0936d95f5d147a1ce15ad6","tid":1659074,"uid":317990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:41:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由10:54 開始</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OhWZavn2OvM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOhWZavn2OvM&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=2b14a4b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OhWZavn2OvM</a><br />\n<br />\n有睇開 Pewds 就知道佢一路以嚟都好重視言論自由 無論係網絡上 或國家法例都會喺片裡面講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJmJGiy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJmJGiy.png&h=b285f507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而計NBA同Blizzard時間之後 國際層面亦多咗好多關注<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coBQ5K5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoBQ5K5.png&h=8b44bb6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1BNoxA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1BNoxA.png&h=87a2ca59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfUbQcH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfUbQcH.png&h=ddb27669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPewdiepie 呢個 Meme Review 系列 雖然將議題講到好似整係得笑話咁<br />\n但睇晒成條片都一定聽到佢語氣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">好明顯係鬧緊中國政權同只識搵錢嘅公司</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcMd3w2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcMd3w2.png&h=f0098bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以佢目的係想通過搞笑少少嘅途徑去引起觀眾關注 呢點Twitter / 國際陣線要留意</span><br />\n<br />\n大家可以做啲乜？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺 Twitter / Youtube comments:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(1) 梗係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大力多謝佢</span></span>啦 最好幽默啲講 例如話會買佢啲merch support 佢咁 (佢冒住冇晒中國嘅fans去笑鳩習大大真係好似維尼喎 唔係唔洗多謝啊???)<br />\n<br />\n(2) 同佢用英文<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">解釋香港情況係點樣</span></span> (條片入面可見 佢都唔係深入了解中港關係 但可以強調人權議題) 更可以俾意見佢話佢可以點繼續支持我哋 (但唔好太forceful)<br />\n<br />\n(3) 做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">文宣</span></span>同外國人講Pewdiepie都支持我哋 (佢連口號都有提過!!!)<br />\n<br />\n最後附上條片出現嗰張手足嘅meme<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJ4jeG5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJ4jeG5.png&h=4434b873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大拿拿幾百萬人睇㗎 今次威出國際啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Liberate Hong Kong<br />\nRevolution of our times&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0a6fa8c6cf3239fad191032aec99fcdb41ada351","tid":1659074,"uid":12569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cfb417f5ea14952d0b19c1bf6b9c7877a3ecd69","tid":1659074,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cfdddfc44cfa0df2299162c7be04c1416e6475","tid":1659074,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20aab512462b1c9c680e63bc812a8ad30ba990c5","tid":1659074,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:47:57.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n國際Connect<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警告!!!<br />\n連登已經被狗同三毛<br />\n嚴重滲透<br />\n加上仲有分化撚<br />\n熱門一片凌亂<br />\n再咁落去唔洗林奠出手<br />\n禁我地網 封鎖連登<br />\n連登就會從內部潰散<br />\n唯有預設不推文回覆<br />\n先可以光復連登</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議所有回覆預設係不推文回覆</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658904</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cbec3998fc12d1db960f99be0294507dca4eef71","tid":1659074,"uid":139316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:51:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛pewdie</span>"},{"pid":"65f04b875c1b8890716296552dd7cd522faaa645","tid":1659074,"uid":317990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:56:55.000Z","msg":"差啲唔記得 Reddit 都重要~~~"},{"pid":"278033b6f3d6d8e35fc00f5cab5bedc93fa516a8","tid":1659074,"uid":285915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:07:06.000Z","msg":"P 牌 照推"},{"pid":"0eea383520c0a5a560f4338f733114c3036e7492","tid":1659074,"uid":285533,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"睇完覺得佢淨係抽下水，根本唔CARE香港"},{"pid":"1b4e21898d7b9e226c7fabae3363b6958ddca4c2","tid":1659074,"uid":105668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215d1bc4ad258d2f988dd24144b8645a844ec04d","tid":1659074,"uid":269811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:25:34.000Z","msg":"推~~"},{"pid":"27e2914dbcde7aeeb8667d78feaa430f8b161bcd","tid":1659074,"uid":105668,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"0eea383520c0a5a560f4338f733114c3036e7492","tid":1659074,"uid":285533,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"睇完覺得佢淨係抽下水，根本唔CARE香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:25:42.000Z","msg":"你都幾貪心，係咪要落埋前線先叫care?你知唔知佢會俾五毛狗攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要佢有幫手解釋個背景，其實已經好好，你睇下LBJ?"},{"pid":"72460229571d9a461ed1393aa610